      <title>花旗的 Kaiser 表示，就业和美联储将在年底前推动股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-02/jobs-fed-to-boost-stocks-into-year-s-end-citi-s-kaiser-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗银行美国股票交易策略主管斯图尔特·凯泽 (Stuart Kaiser) 预计，受就业数据和美联储再次降息的推动，股市将在年底前继续上涨。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-02/jobs-fed-to-boost-stocks-into-year-s-end-citi-s-kaiser-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 14:43:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波罗的海航空公司已制定安全后返回乌克兰的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/airbaltic-has-ready-made-plan-to-fly-back-into-ukraine-once-safe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波罗的海航空公司表示，该公司已制定计划，在乌克兰空域重新开放后短时间内恢复飞往乌克兰的航班。三年前，俄罗斯入侵导致乌克兰空中交通中断。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/airbaltic-has-ready-made-plan-to-fly-back-into-ukraine-once-safe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 14:26:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储需要让路：经济学家萨姆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-02/fed-needs-to-get-out-of-the-way-of-growth-claudia-sahm-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新世纪顾问公司首席经济学家克劳迪娅·萨姆认为，美国经济正在经历“真正的增长回升”，并表示政策制定者必须专注于保持推动美国经济增长的“生产力复兴”。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-02/fed-needs-to-get-out-of-the-way-of-growth-claudia-sahm-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 14:15:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国政府将不经投票通过社会保障法案：LCI TV</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/french-govt-to-adopt-social-security-bill-without-vote-lci-tv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[LCI电视台报道称，法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶将利用宪法工具，在无需议会投票的情况下通过其不受欢迎的预算法案的部分内容。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/french-govt-to-adopt-social-security-bill-without-vote-lci-tv</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 14:01:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英特尔首席执行官基辛格退休，股价大幅上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-02/intel-ceo-gelsinger-retires-stock-rises-sharply-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英特尔公司首席执行官帕特·基辛格已从公司退休并辞去董事会职务，而此时公司正试图实施扭亏为盈计划。受此消息影响，该公司股价大幅上涨。Jonathan Ferro 和 Lisa Abramowicz 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-02/intel-ceo-gelsinger-retires-stock-rises-sharply-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 14:01:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Castle Water 将提供 40 亿英镑股权以拯救泰晤士水务公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/castle-water-to-offer-4-billion-equity-to-rescue-thames-water</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Castle Water Ltd. 本周将向泰晤士水务公司注资 40 亿英镑（51 亿美元），以帮助这家陷入困境的公用事业公司免于破产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/castle-water-to-offer-4-billion-equity-to-rescue-thames-water</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 13:01:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞就预算谈判向巴尼耶施压，法国市场动荡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/french-bonds-fall-as-le-pen-piles-pressure-on-barnier-again</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玛丽娜·勒庞领导的极右翼政党再次威胁称，如果 2025 年预算要求得不到满足，她将推翻政府，法国债券和股票因此承压。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/french-bonds-fall-as-le-pen-piles-pressure-on-barnier-again</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 08:10:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈萨克斯坦民众称欧洲央行将讨论进一步降息 但不确定性较高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/ecb-to-cut-rates-as-inflation-problem-nearly-solved-kazaks-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会成员马丁斯·卡扎克斯表示，欧洲央行下周很可能再次降息，尽管政策制定者将讨论比平时更大幅度的举措，但他们应该谨慎行事。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/ecb-to-cut-rates-as-inflation-problem-nearly-solved-kazaks-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 06:30:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价上涨，焦点是中国经济和 OPEC+ 供应会议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受中国经济缓慢复苏迹象影响，油价上涨，交易员们期待周四的 OPEC+ 会议找到进一步的方向。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 23:28:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>本周数据丰富，美国国债涨势停滞：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/asian-stocks-poised-for-gains-after-best-us-month-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员们准备迎接一系列经济数据和美联储发言人的讲话，这些将有助于影响利率前景，全球最大的债券市场受到冲击，而股市则小幅上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/asian-stocks-poised-for-gains-after-best-us-month-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 22:44:11 GMT</pubDate>
